net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data

Class TableModelCSVConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.internet.http.resource.AbstractResource
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.TableModelCSVConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Resource

    public class TableModelCSVConverter
extends AbstractResource
    This class can be used to produce a CSV file from a TableModel. It gives access as a Resource so it can be used in a variety of ways. The cell values output are determined by the value of String.valueOf() for each cell value with the exception of null which is output as an empty string.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
